## Upcoming Events

### 1st OWASP Lucknow Chapter Meeting
**Date:** [To be announced]  
**Venue:** [To be announced]
**Topic:** Introduction to OWASP & Diving into Application Security  

Join us for the inaugural meeting of OWASP Lucknow! This kickoff event will introduce the chapter, discuss our goals for building a strong local AppSec community, and feature interactive sessions on web application security fundamentals. Whether you're new to security or an experienced professional, this is a great opportunity to connect with fellow security enthusiasts in Lucknow.

**What to expect:**
- Introduction to OWASP and the Lucknow Chapter
- Overview of Application Security
- Interactive discussions and networking
- Q&A session with chapter leaders

Stay tuned for event details!

